# Docker Compose

- Project name: `pdiseg` (compose `name:`).
- Services: `pipeline` (default), `calibrate` + `review` in profile **`tools`**.
- Global flag order: `docker compose --profile tools <subcommand> ...`
- Wrong: `docker compose up --profile tools ...`

Prefer `make docker-up`, `make docker-calibrate`, `make docker-review` for documented env vars (`DATA`, `OUT`, `CALIB`, `PORT`).
